Peace, like air, like sunshine, is something you can benefit from without realizing it, and something you can’t live without. The Chinese military is never absent in safeguarding the world peace.

“For Peace”, released by PLA’s authority, take you to feel the majestic power of the “Fat Girl” Y-20 to deliver relief supplies, to feel the bravery of our Blue Helmet Soldier running forward to protect the kid
To feel the tense atmosphere during the hostage by escort formation in the Gulf of Aden, and to see their daily life of our PLA soldiers.
